{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.100\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">称谢诗。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">颂赞之诗</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.100.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>普天下当向耶和华欢呼！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.100.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>当乐意事奉耶和华，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">当欢唱来到他面前！</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.100.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>当认识耶和华是上帝！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">我们是他造的，也是属他的；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">我们是他的民，是他草场的羊。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.100.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>当称谢进入他的门，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">当赞美进入他的院。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">当感谢他，称颂他的名！</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.100.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>因为耶和华本为善；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">他的慈爱存到永远，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">他的信实直到万代。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}